== 發行 ==
2016年5月，{{link-en|Soda Pictures|Soda Pictures}}買下了電影在英國的發行權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/southside-with-you-uk-release-louis-drax-bafta-amy-hennig-1201762539/|title=Miramax’s ‘Southside With You’ & ‘Louis Drax’ Land UK Distribution; BAFTA To Honor Vidgame Guru Amy Hennig – Global Briefs|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Patrick|last=Hipes|date=May 25, 2016|accessdate=June 21, 2016|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811202249/http://deadline.com/2016/05/southside-with-you-uk-release-louis-drax-bafta-amy-hennig-1201762539/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年6月，[[頂峰娛樂|頂峰娛樂]]獲得了美國的電影發行權，並定於2016年9月2日上映<ref name="release">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/9th-life-of-louis-drax-fall-2016-release-date-1201776464/|title=‘9th Life of Louis Drax’ To Get Theatrical Release This Fall|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Anita|last=Busch|date=June 21, 2016|accessdate=June 21, 2016|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811193301/http://deadline.com/2016/06/9th-life-of-louis-drax-fall-2016-release-date-1201776464/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而英國則於2016年9月9日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.empireonline.com/people/jamie-dornan/new-poster-9th-life-louis-drax/|title=New poster for The 9th Life Of Louis Drax|website=Empire Online|first=James|last=White|date=July 18, 2016|accessdate=July 19, 2016|archive-date=2016-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160719135502/http://www.empireonline.com/people/jamie-dornan/new-poster-9th-life-louis-drax/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反響 ==
電影上映後，收穫了多數的負面評價，[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度41%，基於56條評論，平均分為5.1/10<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_9th_life_of_louis_drax | title=The 9th Life of Louis Drax | accessdate=September 2, 2016 | website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | archive-date=2020-09-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923134631/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_9th_life_of_louis_drax | dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分41，代表「普遍不佳」<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-9th-life-of-louis-drax | title=The 9th Life of Louis Drax | accessdate=September 2, 2016 | website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | archive-date=2016-08-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160831121605/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-9th-life-of-louis-drax | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

